---
import SidebarLayout from '../../../layouts/SidebarLayout.astro';
import "../../../styles/global.css";
---

<SidebarLayout app="c">
  <h1 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-5 text-custom-accent text-center">
    Hello World in C
  </h1>

  <section class="space-y-6 mb-5 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-custom-secondary">
    <p>
      The "Hello World" program is the traditional first program when learning any programming language. 
      It demonstrates the basic syntax and structure of a C program.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-custom-secondary border border-custom rounded-lg p-3 sm:p-4 my-4">
      <pre class="text-xs sm:text-sm overflow-x-auto whitespace-pre-wrap"><code>{`#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
    printf("Hello, World!\\n");
    return 0;
}`}</code></pre>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-custom-accent mt-6 mb-3">Program Breakdown</h2>

    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 pl-4">
      <li><strong class="text-custom-primary">#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;</strong> - Includes the standard input/output library</li>
      <li><strong class="text-custom-primary">int main()</strong> - The main function where program execution begins</li>
      <li><strong class="text-custom-primary">printf()</strong> - Function to print output to the console</li>
      <li><strong class="text-custom-primary">return 0;</strong> - Indicates successful program execution</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="bg-custom-secondary border border-custom rounded-2xl p-4 sm:p-6 mt-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-custom-accent mb-3">Compilation and Execution</h2>
      <p>
        To compile and run this program:
      </p>
      <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 pl-4 mt-2">
        <li>Save the code in a file named <code class="bg-custom-primary text-custom-secondary px-1 rounded text-sm">hello.c</code></li>
        <li>Compile using: <code class="bg-custom-primary text-custom-secondary px-1 rounded text-sm">gcc hello.c -o hello</code></li>
        <li>Run the program: <code class="bg-custom-primary text-custom-secondary px-1 rounded text-sm">./hello</code></li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>
</SidebarLayout>